SpeakBird, using the Android TTS, reads the mentions(and more!) you receive on Twitter.

com.lorenzobraghetto.speakbird.Sync 	-> Android sync related stuff
com.lorenzobraghetto.speakbird.Logic 	-> Application logic stuff
com.lorenzobraghetto.speakbird.View	-> Application View/Activity stuff

I welcome every contribution to this project, via pull request or with suggestion via email (monossido@lorenzobraghetto.com)
Available on Google Play here https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lorenzobraghetto.speakbird, and here the free version https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lorenzobraghetto.speakbirdads
To build SpeakBird you have to use this libraries:

oauth-signpost:
http://code.google.com/p/oauth-signpost/ (signpost-commonshttp signpost-core)

twitter4j:
http://twitter4j.org/en/index.html

ActionBarSherlock:
http://actionbarsherlock.com/

Android-PullToRefresh:
https://github.com/chrisbanes/Android-PullToRefresh

UrlImageViewHelper:
https://github.com/koush/UrlImageViewHelper

